name: Ouity
description:
Second stop of my Interstellar Journey; After getting here, a lot of things didn't make sense; it seemed deserted, but if that was the case, who or what turned on all of these lights? Who uses these primitive cars? I don't know if I'll ever find out, but the place gives off a weird vibe, … I feel like I belong here, or more so, like I own here.
